node.text: Follow This Tastemaker 💘 The signature style by DC-based designer @zoefeldmandesign and her inspired renovations are taking Georgetown by storm. Follow along to see her #Chairish picks and get all her ideas for incorporating her style in your own spaces via the link in our bio! #foundandchairished {#interiordesign by #ChairishTradeMember @zoefeldmandesign, 📷 by @stacyzaringoldberg}
